data.description: Desirable one-level on a corner lot in a prime Newberg location! Freshly painted, meticulously maintained & thoughtful layout. Open kitchen & living area w high ceilings & eye-catching gas fireplace. Master suite w double closets. Generous 2nd bed w arched window perch & private patio. Attached 2 car garage w stand-up storage space above. Private, fenced backyard w pavers. Close to George Fox & historic downtown. Reasonable HOA dues!
